{"tid":1242904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載高登] 疑似醫管局官方文件顯示病人資料同警察內部系統連結","createTime":"2019-06-19T08:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T10:37:05.000Z","uid":36592,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfc4377a1b46c51919cbb11b1255a03b2cf6b0e","tid":1242904,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:49:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7072535&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7072535%26page%3D1&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=d2debf3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7072535&amp;page=1</a><br />\n入面有更多資料比各位查證<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/18/9OeGD4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F18%2F9OeGD4.png&h=49463930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/18/dAsXPE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F18%2FdAsXPE.png&h=efe1ebbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/18/5SIZr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F18%2F5SIZr4.png&h=d9138ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/19/0fZHIz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F0fZHIz.png&h=7571da86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人懷疑時間順序可能係咁：<br />\n1. eSARS 通報系統<br />\n2. HA出memo叫人落tag<br />\n3. 警犬鎮壓<br />\n4. 傷者入院<br />\n5. 有醫護跟memo落tag<br />\n6. 警犬拉人<br />\n<br />\n如果醫管局同警務署有合作, 就代表呢個係司長級行動。  食物及衛生局同保安局都係政務司既。  咁樣代表打壓係更高層。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">張建宗陳肇始李家超請立即交代</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cc865bd217f139cf18a98de1fcedeff1de53fc","tid":1242904,"uid":36592,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"陳醫生跟進緊，請各位集氣支持陳醫生同前線醫護人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2236059276668123/posts/2374737549466961/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2236059276668123%2Fposts%2F2374737549466961%2F&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=698a9dbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2236059276668123/posts/2374737549466961/</a>"},{"pid":"85c8e93f20f639ca2ca83723e0cc71dffaed8c58","tid":1242904,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:54:04.000Z","msg":"其實呢d野係咪689時期已經有<br />\n定係689指示要做？<br />\n<br />\n張建宗應該又話乜都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26541ef7b5c2596aebdc17a77aac83093bbd5e4a","tid":1242904,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:54:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7bff3a6183e7feeeb51b2b6e4aa8a3865f06e7c1","tid":1242904,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"又要睇記者招待會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee57e9a33730dddb9a4269c3b2846946e7b10d8","tid":1242904,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fc20a3dfb0ced550c22a1926510bc8363803bf3","tid":1242904,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85c8e93f20f639ca2ca83723e0cc71dffaed8c58","tid":1242904,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:54:04.000Z","msg":"其實呢d野係咪689時期已經有<br />\n定係689指示要做？<br />\n<br />\n張建宗應該又話乜都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:01:33.000Z","msg":"射番個波比689<