":193237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3974eb2195c2faeec447d5042eaa270128657a87","tid":1242904,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"醫管局就陳沛然的言論作嚴正澄清指，MIIDSS是警務處掌管，2003年香港爆發SARS疫情亦是透過相關系統的運算能力進行接觸追查，<span style=\"color: red;\">而有關資料是透過加密形式以電郵傳送，醫管局電腦系統與警方MIIDSS電腦系統從來沒有任何聯繫</span>。醫管局稱，在SARS疫情之後，醫管局再沒有類似形式的資料傳送。他們又希望，有關病人私隱的評論，均建基於事實，避免打擊醫患關係，影響病人信心。"},{"pid":"4cacdb9261231cc6084555ba0156ed3ac2ad3184","tid":1242904,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fab013616f640812ba0c05152da60122ef058a26","tid":1242904,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"推翻上水面 未解決！"},{"pid":"c3f6119caf82e76f77cfdc8e6fe0a29725b849e8","tid":1242904,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d242b5156fda06bdf9ea041ab5a19571952c03a","tid":1242904,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"不了了之"},{"pid":"c92cfe77c695f7d79e755ee780555d0b52b6a72c","tid":1242904,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"702fe2f1a90e89ef418b80800f37c948efbf5c00","tid":1242904,"uid":268650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"79aeacb38f7f520fcd5e07a2e8f6ca0927b13966","tid":1242904,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以畀佢哋走甩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Gm2av1y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F